[0.381, "o", "Mail account ready: agent-b@om-mail.local (provider: localdir)\r\nSigning public key: PX4hn24X3iL5LVc6-wLAzCN1ytPZ7aZzWLpqKvA606c\r\nShare the address and public key with peers; they pin them with `om mail peers add`.\r\nFor context packs, exchange a shared key out of band: `om mail peers new-shared-key`.\r\n"]
[1.413, "o", "Share this key out of band (password manager, in person) — never over email.\r\nBoth sides store it with `om mail peers add ADDRESS --key PUBKEY --shared-key KEY`.\r\n"]
[0.012, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m# Pin each other: address + public key + shared key, exchanged out of band.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
